#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:21
msgid "Über MyTools"
msgstr "About MyTools"

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:24
msgid ""
"MyTools ist eine persönliche Tool-Zentrale für Alltag, Homelab, Streaming "
"und kleine Web-Helfer. Die App bündelt Schnellzugriffe, Wetter, Notizen, "
"Rechner, Dashboards und Mini-Games in einer modernen Django-Oberfläche."
msgstr ""
"MyTools is a personal hub for everyday tasks, homelabs, streaming, and small "
"web tools. The app combines shortcuts, weather, notes, calculators, "
"dashboards, and mini-games in a modern Django interface."

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:33
msgid "Zur Startseite"
msgstr "Back to homepage"

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:38 .\app\templates\app\home.html:177
msgid "Notizen öffnen"
msgstr "Open Notes"

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:48
msgid "Alles an einem Ort"
msgstr "Everything in one place"

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:51
msgid ""
"Von lokalen Server-Links bis zu API-Tools: MyTools soll die wichtigsten "
"kleinen Helfer zentral, schnell erreichbar und angenehm bedienbar machen."
msgstr ""
"From local server links to API tools: MyTools is designed to make the most "
"important small helpers centrally accessible, quick to find, and easy to use."

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:62
msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard"

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:63
msgid "Shortcuts, Favoriten, Bereiche und Drag & Drop"
msgstr "Shortcuts, Favorites, Panels, and Drag & Drop"

