msgstr "Design"

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:75
msgid "Dark Mode, Theme-Editor und responsive Layouts"
msgstr "Dark Mode, Theme Editor, and Responsive Layouts"

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:85
msgid "Schnellzugriffe"
msgstr "Quick Links"

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:88
msgid ""
"Eigene Links können mit Icons, Bildern, Favoriten und Kategorien gespeichert "
"werden. Bereiche lassen sich sortieren, einklappen und farblich markieren."
msgstr ""
"You can save your own links with icons, images, favorites, and categories. "
"Sections can be sorted, collapsed, and color-coded."

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:100
msgid "OBS & Streaming"
msgstr "OBS & Streaming"

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:103
msgid ""
"Das OBS Dashboard verbindet sich mit OBS WebSocket und kann Szenen, Quellen, "
"Audio, Aufnahme und Streaming lokal steuern."
msgstr ""
"The OBS Dashboard connects to OBS WebSocket and can control scenes, sources, "
"audio, recording, and streaming locally."

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:115
msgid "Mini-Tools & Games"
msgstr "Mini-Tools & Games"

#: .\app\templates\app\about.html:118
msgid ""
"Einheitenrechner, Human Benchmark, Avatar Wiki, Notizen und Drift Circuit "
"Pro erweitern das Dashboard um praktische und spielerische Funktionen."
msgstr ""
"Unit Converter, Human Benchmark, Avatar Wiki, Notes, and Drift Circuit Pro "
"add practical and fun features to the dashboard."

